sequenceDiagram
    actor Applicant
    participant Frontend
    participant Gateway
    participant AuthService

    Applicant->>Frontend: Open signup page and enter details
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /gateway/auth/signup
    Gateway->>AuthService: POST /api/auth/signup
    AuthService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (user created)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK (success)
    Frontend-->>Applicant: Show signup success and navigate to login

    Applicant->>Frontend: Enter email/password on login page
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /gateway/auth/login
    Gateway->>AuthService: POST /api/auth/login
    AuthService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (token, role, user info)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK (auth response)
    Frontend-->>Frontend: Store token/session in sessionStorage
    Frontend-->>Applicant: Redirect to /dashboard or /admin based on role
